trans-unit.source: Exposes <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.ControlType.Document"></xref> control types to [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Viser <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.ControlType.Document"> </xref> kontrollere målgruppeattributtet [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The DocumentAutomationPeer represents documents and supports the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>.
trans-unit.target: DocumentAutomationPeer representerer dokumenter og støtter <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>

trans-unit.source: Objects such as a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument> or <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> can contain embedded objects, such as images and hyperlinks.
trans-unit.target: Objekter som en <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument>eller <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>kan inneholde innebygde objekter, for eksempel bilder og hyperkoblinger.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument>

trans-unit.source: Initially, when you try to get the child elements of the document, <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName> does not return the embedded objects.
trans-unit.target: I utgangspunktet når du prøver å få underordnet elementer i dokumentet, <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>returnerer ikke innebygde objekter.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To get the embedded elements, obtain a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> from the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern> and call <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: For å få de innebygde elementene, hente en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange>fra <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>og kall <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange>

trans-unit.source: After <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is called, any elements in that <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> are returned by <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Etter <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>kalles alle elementer i som <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange>returneres av <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Unless you know the document is a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>, you should not call <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A> on the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern.DocumentRange%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Hvis du ikke vet dokumentet er en <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>, du kan ikke kalle <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A>på den <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern.DocumentRange%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern.DocumentRange%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>

trans-unit.source: If the document is loaded from a network location, calling <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A> on the entire document is resource intensive.
trans-unit.target: Hvis dokumentet er lastet inn fra en nettverksplassering, kaller <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A>på hele dokumentet er ressursen dataintensive.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A>

trans-unit.source: Instead, you should use one of the methods on <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern> that returns a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> that represents a portion of the document.
trans-unit.target: I stedet, bør du bruke én av metodene på <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>som returnerer en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange>som representerer en del av dokumentet.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>

trans-unit.source: This property does not indicate whether the element is visible.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen angir ikke om elementet er synlig.

trans-unit.source: In some circumstances, an element is on the screen but is still not visible.
trans-unit.target: I noen tilfeller kan vises på skjermen for et element, men er fremdeles ikke er synlig.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the element is obscured by other elements, it might not be visible.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis elementet er skjult av andre elementer, kan den ikke være synlig.

trans-unit.source: In this case, the method returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet metoden returnerer `false`.
